modName: Breezehome Additions (First mod on nexus for me)
summary: Adds a new room to breezehome. In the new room there is an anvil, crafting table, and knife sharpener. There's also an addition to the room with the alchemy table. I added an arcane enchanter. First mod on nexus for me. Check out the video in the videos section!
descriptionHtml: Adds a new room to breezewood. In the new room there is a anvil, crafting table, and knife sharpener. There's also an addition to the room with the alchemy table. I added an arcane enchanter. I also moved the bed and somethings around in order to get some space. But now you have everyhting in your breezehome except skyforge. This is my first mod.
author: aswag5
